  <div class="card-grid">
    {% for c in calcs %}{% if c.cat == cat.name %}
    <a class="calc-card" href="/{{ c.slug }}/">
      <span class="calc-card-icon" aria-hidden="true">{{ c.icon }}</span>
      <span class="calc-card-name">{{ c.name }}</span>
      <span class="calc-card-short">{{ c.short }}</span>
    </a>
    {% endif %}{% endfor %}
  </div>
  {% endfor %}

  <section class="prose" style="margin-top:3rem;">
    <h2>Why CalculateMoney?</h2>
    <p><strong>Accurate methods, stated openly.</strong> Every calculator explains its formula and assumptions on the page — the FD calculator compounds quarterly like Indian banks do, the RD calculator computes per-instalment interest the way the post office does, and the income tax calculator applies the Section 87A rebate, surcharge and marginal relief exactly as the Finance Act 2025 prescribes.</p>
    <p><strong>Type or slide.</strong> Enter exact amounts like ₹4,83,250 or drag a slider to explore. Results, charts and year-by-year tables update instantly — and the link in your address bar always reproduces your exact calculation, so you can save or share it.</p>
    <p><strong>Free and private.</strong> No login, no personal data collected by the calculators — everything runs in your browser. These tools are for education and planning; for major decisions, verify with a qualified advisor.</p>
  </section>
